wikipedia_page.main: Kossuth William Duncan (29 July 1857 – 30 June 1919) was a South Australian miller and politician. He was a member of the South Australian Legislative Council for Northern District from 1900 to 1902 and a member of the South Australian House of Assembly for Stanley from 1907 to 1910. He was later mayor of the Corporate Town of Laura from 1913 to 1914.
